      <title>佩特罗寻求与哥伦比亚腐败丑闻保持距离</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/petro-seeks-to-distance-himself-from-colombian-graft-scandal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哥伦比亚总统古斯塔沃·佩特罗表示，该国机构存在“结构性腐败”，他试图与最近涉及盟友的贿赂丑闻撇清关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/petro-seeks-to-distance-himself-from-colombian-graft-scandal</guid>
