    <item>
      <title>拜登强化 2024 年焦点，白宫提拔新闻助理</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/white-house-promotes-press-aides-as-biden-sharpens-2024-focus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在新闻秘书卡琳·让-皮埃尔的高级副手离职后，白宫正在提拔两名长期新闻助理，作为在乔·拜登总统竞选连任之前加强新闻办公室运营的努力的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/white-house-promotes-press-aides-as-biden-sharpens-2024-focus</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 23:34:02 GMT</pubDate>
